name: UNCEASING VIXEN 22:13
description: A nude female study from the photographic series titled Unceasing Vixens.  This image was created with a DSLR camera but was manipulated to look like it was taken with film. A vixen is a fox and by definition is a spirited or fierce woman, specifically one seen as sexually attractive. This image could only be obtained from collecting another Unceasing Vixen.
